From b75e4010b831a0f98342dc9a78cf59df8d840ad0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Luasz Spintzyk <lukasz.spintzyk@synaptics.com>
Date: Tue, 13 Jan 2026 13:49:51 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 12/28] Detect xe exported gem object without vmap/vunmap
 callbacks and use proper vmap/vunmap implementation for them

---
 ci/build_against_kernel |  2 +-
 module/Kconfig          |  1 +
